{"tid":662994,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"寫app一問 for一特別既工種類似抄散","createTime":"2018-05-13T01:56:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T02:50:35.000Z","uid":115140,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"77ec69d322d6209ce20fa2fc24f34e474bd6afd3","tid":662994,"uid":115140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T01:56:10.000Z","msg":"有無巴打做過寫類似抄散既app?  <br />\n<br />\n我無喇喇有個諗法就係寫一個app for特別既工種，例如救生員咁<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n因為呢一行係搵人同請人係呢幾十年都無進步，亦都唔想再有俾盤頭呃既新章仔，或者保障返盤頭請一啲有質素既救生員，暫時都有幾多諗法，講出幾個嚟俾大家諗諗可唔可行<br />\n<br />\n1. <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">提供平台俾雙方俾工/人</span></span><br />\n會有今年既公價俾大家睇睇，俾大家參考返，亦有pm 功能俾大家傾個價錢，等等，仲要唔洗再入十幾個wtsgroup日日俾人洗喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2.<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">盤頭</span></span><br />\nApp會有一啲關於盤頭同救生員既資料，例如：放飛機，玩手機，俾會所頭訴等等，一定要講個價錢出嚟，唔講出嚟，咁你即係搵義務更？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">救生員</span></span><br />\n相反救生員都會知道返盤頭既資料，例如：拖糧，唔出人工等等，放飛機，盤頭可以記錄返，咁你既分數就咁低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n4.<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">泳池資料</span></span><br />\n會有點去，圖片，要求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n更上更落？定二人池？等等基本資料<br />\n<br />\n5.<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">急更</span></span><br />\n相信做緊盤頭最煩就係搵急更，你一係app搵急更，app就send你急更俾附近得閑既師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n6.<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">分身</span></span><br />\n一定要用救生咭做申請，咁就唔怕無限分身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n7.<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">糧</span></span><br />\n<br />\n放工即pay,我地會幫盤頭俾住先，<br />\n<br />\n呢啲都只係一啲諗法，不過其實落真係無乜特別.....但起碼幫到呢一行，唔會仲好似十幾年前咁，拖糧啊，黑心盤頭，盤頭成日俾人放飛機，幫下大家搵近屋企既池！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"264820399447c9a5e87c7b623d0ba22d8e0f22b0","tid":662994,"uid":65462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T02:02:22.000Z","msg":"睇你出幾錢，冇人做義工"},{"pid":"792ba4af442d4a66097069fb7d1bfcad8f34c86a","tid":662994,"uid":115140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"264820399447c9a5e87c7b623d0ba22d8e0f22b0","tid":662994,"uid":65462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T02:02:22.000Z","msg":"睇你出幾錢，冇人做義工"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T02:07:08.000Z","msg":"我知，可能會自己寫，畢竟仲係學生哥，無錢就要自己嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60c24352171de2ac60ea58790b2def634b00c4d9","tid":662994,"uid":26474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T02:21:17.000Z","msg":"判頭呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"a5239cc3d47f1a16112c2a51b85b44b0e7a5769e","tid":662994,"uid":161230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T02:32:52.000Z","msg":"你幫人比錢。咁人地走數咁點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92d090f8c060a3c39df3fd7057f4d5bb4a9b173d","tid":662994,"uid":172684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T02:39:18.000Z","msg":"創科局 八段錦"},{"pid":"3e901889264bc273803971a0ca30e6bf4134065c","tid":662994,"uid":10009,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T02:50:54.000Z","msg":"地盤工就寫微信小程序啦<br />\n地盤佬一定有微信<br />\n你叫佢地下載多一個app佢地仲嫌煩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然我都唔鐘意wechat<br />\n但要配合target audience就無計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c9c7c5ee798f47d921f97810b909378897060af","tid":662994,"uid":85524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77ec69d322d6209ce20fa2fc24f34e474bd6afd3","tid":662